name: Bean spawner 2 | The Beaning
description:
You play as the mythic "David The Bean" And your goal is to be the best bean in Beanland. Spawn Your beans every where by pressing space and be the true bestest bean. Traverse places like the random trees and the 2 really big walls. Conquer the mighty red beanpot with the mythic "OG Bean" How much bean, can you bean?

(This image is from Bean spawner 1)
